{"tid":2042130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國將於7月6日重開羅浮宮博物館","createTime":"2020-05-29T16:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T16:25:08.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db11e791c3baf65224f8744b7d98a8421796a356","tid":2042130,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"法國將於7月6日重開羅浮宮博物館<br />\n2020-05-30 HKT 00:10<br />\n<br />\n法國的新型肺炎疫情持續緩和，位於首都巴黎的羅浮宮博物館宣布，將於7月6日重開。<br />\n<br />\n羅浮宮博物館因應疫情，自3月中起關閉。羅浮宮表示，重開後會推出預約系統，並要求遊客參觀時戴口罩，及保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n法國目前有超過18萬人確診感染新型肺炎，超過28000人死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529217-20200530.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529217-20200530.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=10024e8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529217-20200530.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=66caa76f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529217-20200530.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}